+  </message>
+  <message name="IDS_BROWSER_DCL_MEMORY_RESTRICTED" desc="Text that explains to the user that dynamic code loading via memory restricted.">
+    Dynamic code loading via memory is restricted.
+  </message>
+  <message name="IDS_BROWSER_DCL_MEMORY_RESTRICTED_WITH_LINK" desc="Text at the top of the Website list, explaining to the user that dynamic code loading via memory restricted. Contains a link to the settings menu to change it.">
+    Dynamic code loading via memory for <ph name="APP_NAME">%1$s<ex>Vanadium</ex></ph> is currently restricted, which can be allowed at <ph name="BEGIN_LINK">&lt;link&gt;</ph>Android Settings<ph name="END_LINK">&lt;/link&gt;</ph>.
+  </message>
 </grit-part>
